Presenting gg_tesla.

Uses a variety of custom textures, self-illuminating textures, reflective textures, etc.

This map was mostly an experimentation of all sorts of colored textures, how to create the .vmt files associated with textures. Also, this was a experimentation in cell-shading.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created by myself.
